        "key": "55af52dc-7f51-4365-ad55-52098f445648",
        "markdown": "# 8: Feature Integration\n\nThe release window is opening soon, and your team has three finished features sitting on separate branches: `feature/login-ui`, `feature/api-endpoints`, and `docs/api-guide`. \n\nYour team lead wants all of these integrated into the `main` branch. Thankfully, the developers communicated well, and there shouldn't be any merge conflicts. Your goal is to cleanly merge all three branches into `main` so the QA team can test the complete build.\n\n## Objectives\n\n1. Checkout to the `main` branch.\n2. Merge the `feature/login-ui` branch into `main`.\n3. Merge the `feature/api-endpoints` branch into `main`.\n4. Merge the `docs/api-guide` branch into `main`.\n\n> **Note:** If you are having trouble with VIM. Use `:wq` to write & quit the editor or use the `--no-edit` merge flag to circumvent commit message editing.",
